           SHORT="The base set of plugins for Gstreamer"

cat << EOF
gst-plugins-base is a well-groomed and well-maintained collection of GStreamer
plug-ins and elements, spanning the range of possible types of elements one
would want to write for GStreamer. It also contains helper libraries and base
classes useful for writing elements. A wide range of video and audio decoders,
encoders, and filters are included.
EOF
